OL,3,CRailway town named Britain's most
OL,4,Caffordable for families to buy a home
OL,6,FShildon in the North East has been
OL,7,Fnamed as the most affordable town in
OL,8,FBritain for families looking to buy a
OL,9,Fhome.
OL,11,FZoopla, which carried out the
OL,12,Fresearch, compared average prices for
OL,13,Fthree-bedroom homes with estimated
OL,14,Fearnings for couples working full-time.
OL,16,FTowns in northern England, Scotland
OL,17,Fand Wales dominated the top of the
OL,18,Faffordability rankings, which were
OL,19,Fbased on 300 towns that are popular
OL,20,Fwith people looking to buy family-
OL,21,Fsized homes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
