FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774231379
OL,3,CRailway town named Britain's most
OL,4,Caffordable for families to buy a home
OL,6,FShildon, Co Durham, topped the list
OL,7,Fwith an average house price-to-
OL,8,Fearnings ratio of 1.36.
OL,10,FIn Wales, Ferndale in the Rhondda
OL,11,FValley was named as the most
OL,12,Faffordable town for families, with
OL,13,Fhomes there costing around 1.85 times
OL,14,Fearnings.
OL,16,FIn Scotland, Cumnock in East Ayrshire
OL,17,Fwas placed top, with three-bedroom
OL,18,Fhomes costing around 1.68 times dual
OL,19,Fwages.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
