OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774231379
OL,3,CRailway town named Britain's most
OL,4,Caffordable for families to buy a home
OL,6,FRichard Donnell, executive director at
OL,7,FZoopla, said: "The housing market is
OL,8,Fentering one of its busiest periods,
OL,9,Fwith the most homes for sale in many
OL,10,Fyears and at a time when buyers are
OL,11,Fbecoming increasingly focused on value
OL,12,Ffor money.
OL,14,F"What stands out is the scale of the
OL,15,Faffordability gap across the UK. In
OL,16,Fparts of the North East, families can
OL,17,Fbuy a home for much less than the cost
OL,18,Fof buying in the most affordable towns
OL,19,Fin southern England.
OL,26,@oD@OOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774231379
OL,3,CRailway town named Britain's most
OL,4,Caffordable for families to buy a home
OL,6,F"While there are affordable options in
OL,7,Fevery region, buyers often face a
OL,8,Ftrade-off between lower house prices
OL,9,Fand their proximity to major
OL,10,Femployment centres.
OL,12,F"Many of the most affordable towns in
OL,13,Fsouthern England are coastal, meaning
OL,14,Fbetter affordability may come at the
OL,15,Fcost of more expensive travel which
OL,16,Fmay not work for everyone."
