OL,6,FMortgage rates have jumped in recent
OL,7,Fweeks as the conflict in the Middle
OL,8,FEast has affected financial markets
OL,9,Fand prompted expectations that
OL,10,Finflation in the months ahead could be
OL,11,Fhigher than previously expected.
OL,13,FHere are the 10 most affordable towns
OL,14,Fin Zoopla's analysis, ranked in order
OL,15,Fof the house-price to earnings ratio,
OL,16,Fwith the average value of a three-
OL,17,Fbedroom home followed by the average
OL,18,Fhouse price-to-earnings ratio for
OL,19,Ffamilies:
OL,21,F1. Shildon, North East, #82,500, 1.36
